---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - HighProtein Foodz">
  <Header />
  <section class="page-content fade-in-on-scroll">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="page-lede">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <p>By accessing or using HighProtein Foodz ("the Website"), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.</p>

      <h2>Use of the Website</h2>
      <p>HighProtein Foodz provides a <strong>high protein foods list</strong> and nutrition database for informational and educational purposes. You may use this website for personal, non-commercial purposes. You agree not to reproduce, distribute, or exploit our content for commercial gain without our written consent.</p>

      <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
      <p>While we strive to ensure all nutrition data on our <strong>protein foods list</strong> is accurate and up-to-date, we make no warranties regarding the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of this information. Nutrition data is sourced from USDA FoodData Central and may vary by brand, preparation method, and source. Always consult a qualified healthcare professional for dietary advice.</p>

      <h2>Pricing Information</h2>
      <p>Prices shown on our website are average estimates and may not reflect current market prices. We are not responsible for any discrepancies between listed prices and actual prices at retailers. <strong>Low calorie high protein foods</strong> and other categories are labeled based on general nutritional guidelines and may vary.</p>

      <h2>No Medical Advice</h2>
      <p>The information provided on HighProtein Foodz is for informational purposes only and is not intended as medical advice. We do not diagnose, treat, or prevent any health condition. Always consult with a qualified healthcare provider before making significant changes to your diet, especially when following a <strong>high protein diet</strong> for weight loss or other health purposes.</p>

      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and data compilations, is the property of HighProtein Foodz and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. Our curated <strong>protein rich foods</strong> database, sorting tools, and analysis represent original work.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>HighProtein Foodz and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of or inability to use this website. This includes reliance on nutrition data for meal planning, <strong>healthy high protein meals</strong>, or dietary decisions.</p>

      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>Our website may contain links to external sites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of these third-party websites. We encourage you to review their terms and policies.</p>

      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms & Conditions at any time. Changes become effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use of the website after modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws, without regard to conflict of law provisions.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these Terms & Conditions, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    min-height: 100dvh;
  }

  .page-content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .page-lede {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .page-content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .page-content a {
    color: var(--accent-green);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .page-content a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-green-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .page-content {
      padding: 5rem 0 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>